@stetsonblaylockfishing starting the final day of the @bass_nation Classic out strong! 💪 How bout that Hard Knocker coming in clutch?!? #bassmasterclassic 
Video credit: @bass_nation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on August 19, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and outdoors.

node.text:
The BOOYAH ToadRunner has a bendable tail 💪 that lets you change the sound, action and speed of the bait. Plop, plop, plop = BOOM! 😎 Move some water and bring 'em to you....
📸: @rawrfishing #bassfishing #topwater

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on August 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and body of water.

node.text:
Here's 5.64 reasons (all in pounds 😏) why @pbf_fishing throws a BOOYAH Pad Crasher 🐸 at his secret NY bassin' spot.... Awesome pic and fish, dude!
#bassfishing #topwater

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on August 17, 2021. May be an image of body of water.

node.text:
You think this one wanted @jmasonfishing's BOOYAH Mobster Swim Jig? 🎯 Choked it!
#bassfishing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by BOOYAH Bait Co. on August 13, 2021 tagging @christiefishing. May be an image of body of water.

node.text:
Now @christiefishing is just showing off LOL. Got himself another 1-cast double with a BOOYAH Boss Pop 😳 and a couple good ones at that! 🔥 Fire up the school, baby!!
#topwater #bassfishing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and body of water.

node.text:
How about @jetterfishing and @bassnwiththeboss doing a little family bonding 💯 and they even let a BOOYAH XCS Series squarebill tag along?!?! 🙌 Love it, fellas!
#bassfishing

node.text:
Yup, this looks like a good place to throw the "albino frog" color BOOYAH Pad Crasher 👀 and @zastrow_14 confirmed it. 👊 Great fish, dude!
#topwater #bassfishing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on July 27, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and body of water.

node.text:
The 🔨 @christiefishing says you've "gotta do what you gotta do to get your favorite bait back...." 😎 In this case a BOOYAH Mobster swim jig – know it catches 'em when Jason is willing to (potentially) fight off snakes to retrieve it LOL.
#bassfishing

node.text: Typical sight when they eat the BOOYAH Mobster Swim Jig‼️ #MWM

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on July 23, 2021. May be an image of fishing rod and body of water.

node.text:
Now here's some proven fish-catchers!!! The “Elite 3 Pack” includes BOOYAH's top-3 hard baits in model and color 🎯 and saves you $$$! Comes with:

► 1/2-oz Hard Knocker (Rayburn red)
► 2" Boss Pop (bone shiner)
► XCS100 squarebill (perch)

MSRP of $18.99 and will be at all retail. 👊
#bassfishing

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on July 21, 2021.

node.text: "Tommy Gun" is our perch pattern in the BOOYAH Mobster Swim Jig. Perfect for burnin' over shallow flats in early summer or fishing around spawners! 🔥 #MWM

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BOOYAH Bait Co. on July 15, 2021. May be an image of body of water.

node.text:
The Mobster Swim Jig has been catching bass in the "prototype" stage for well over two years now! 🔨🔨

Built with a unique tapered head design that comes through cover like none other on the market. 👊
